name: Internet Money (BSC)
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Internet Money (IM) was created to serve as a form of peer to peer "digital cash". The contract is simple:
you can buy, sell, send and burn IM. Internet Money has no admin keys, no taxes, no reflections and is
deflationary. Cryptocurrency was created to be a decentralized way to interact with money. We aim to take continual steps towards the decentralization of every facet of the Internet Money ecosystem; because we believe this is the way money should be:
No centralized entities.
No controlling forces.
Power in the hands of the people.
